# HA Add-on Boilerplate - Project Overview

## Purpose
A boilerplate/starter template for building Home Assistant add-ons with a modern full-stack TypeScript architecture.

## Core Stack
- **Backend**: Node.js + Express + TypeScript + Prisma ORM + WebSocket
- **Frontend**: React + TypeScript + Vite
- **Database**: PostgreSQL
- **Infrastructure**: pnpm workspaces, Docker, Home Assistant ingress

## Key Features
- Full-stack TypeScript with shared types between client and server
- Real-time WebSocket communication
- HA ingress support for seamless panel integration
- Prisma ORM with migration support
- Dark-themed responsive UI with CSS variables
- Structured logging system
- Docker multi-stage build for HA deployment
